\c 28
\s UIsaka uthuma uJakobe eHarani
\p
\v 1 UIsaka wasebiza uJakobe, wambusisa, wamlaya wathi kuye: Ungathathi umfazi kumadodakazi eKhanani\x + 24.3.\x*.
\v 2 Sukuma\x + Hos. 12.12.\x* uye ePadani-Arama\x + 25.20; 48.7.\x*, endlini kaBethuweli\x + 22.23.\x* uyise kanyoko, uzithathele khona umfazi kumadodakazi kaLabani umalumakho\x + 24.29.\x*.
\v 3 Njalo uNkulunkulu uSomandla akubusise, akwenze ube lenzalo akwandise, ukuze ube ngumbuthano wezizwe\x + 17.1.\x*;
\v 4 abesekupha isibusiso sikaAbrahama\x + 12.2.\x*, kuwe lenzalweni yakho kanye lawe\x + 28.1,3.\x*, ukuze udle ilifa lelizwe lapho ohlala khona njengowezizwe\f + \fk njengowezizwe: \fl Heb. \fq ilizwe lokuhlala kwakho njengowezizwe.\f*, uNkulunkulu alinika uAbrahama.
\v 5 UIsaka wasethuma uJakobe waya ePadani-Arama kuLabani indodana kaBethuweli umSiriya, umfowabo kaRebeka unina kaJakobe loEsawu.
\p
\v 6 UEsawu wasebona ukuthi uIsaka umbusisile uJakobe\x + 28.1,3.\x*, wamthuma ePadani-Arama ukuze azithathele khona umfazi, lapho embusisa wamlaya esithi: Ungathathi umfazi kumadodakazi eKhanani;
\v 7 lokuthi uJakobe walalela oyise lonina, waya ePadani-Arama.
\v 8 UEsawu wasebona ukuthi amadodakazi eKhanani ayemabi emehlweni kaIsaka uyise\x + 24.3; 26.35.\x*.
\v 9 Ngakho uEsawu waya kuIshmayeli, wazithathela uMahalathi\x + 36.3; 26.34.\x* indodakazi kaIshmayeli, indodana kaAbrahama, udadewabo kaNebayothi\x + 25.13; 36.3.\x*, abe ngumka\add khe\add* phezu kwabafazi ayelabo.
\s Iphupho likaJakobe eseBhetheli
\p
\v 10 UJakobe wasephuma eBherishebha\x + 26.23,33.\x* waya eHarani\x + Seb. 7.2.\x*.
\v 11 Wafika endaweni, achitha khona ubusuku ngoba ilanga lalitshonile. Wasethatha \add ilitshe\add* ematsheni aleyondawo, wenza umqamelo wakhe, walala kuleyondawo.
\v 12 Waphupha\x + 37.5,9; 40.5; 41.1. Jobe 33.15.\x*, khangela-ke, ilele limisiwe emhlabeni, isihloko salo sifinyelela emazulwini, khangela-ke, ingilosi zikaNkulunkulu zisenyuka zisehla kulo\x + Joha. 1.51.\x*.
\v 13 Khangela-ke, iN\nd kosi\nd* yema phezu kwalo\x + 35.1; 48.3.\x*, yathi: NgiyiN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu kaAbrahama uyihlo loNkulunkulu kaIsaka\x + 26.24; 24.12.\x*; ilizwe olele kulo, ngizakunika lona, lenzalo yakho\x + 13.15.\x*;
\v 14 njalo inzalo yakho izakuba ngangothuli lomhlaba\x + 13.16.\x*, uzasabalalela entshonalanga lempumalanga lenyakatho leningizimu\x + 13.14. Dute. 12.20.\x*; njalo zizabusiswa kuwe zonke insendo zomhlaba, lasenzalweni yakho\x + 12.3; 18.18; 22.18; 26.4.\x*.
\v 15 Khangela-ke, ngilawe\x + 26.24; 31.3; 28.20.\x*, ngizakulondoloza kuzo zonke \add indawo\add* lapha oya khona, ngikubuyise kulelilizwe\x + 35.6.\x*; ngoba kangiyikukutshiya\x + Dute. 31.6,8. Josh. 1.5. 1 Kho. 8.57. 1 Lan. 28.20. Heb. 13.5.\x* ngize ngikwenze lokho engikhulume ngakho kuwe.
\v 16 Kwathi uJakobe ephaphama ebuthongweni bakhe, wathi: Isibili iN\nd kosi\nd* ikulindawo\x + Eks. 3.5. Josh. 5.15.\x*, mina-ke benginga\add kw\add*azi.
\v 17 Wasesesaba wathi: Yesabeka kangakanani lindawo! Kayisilutho ngaphandle kokuthi yindlu kaNkulunkulu, laleli lisango lamazulu.
\v 18 UJakobe wasevuka ekuseni kakhulu, wathatha ilitshe alenza laba ngumqamelo wakhe, walimisa laba yinsika\x + 31.13,45; 35.14. 2 Sam. 18.18.\x*, wathela amagcobo phezu kwesihloko salo\x + Levi 8.10,11. Nani 7.1.\x*.
\v 19 Wasebiza ibizo laleyondawo iBhetheli\x + Hlu. 1.23,26.\x*\f + \fk iBhetheli: \fl okuyikuthi, \fq indlu kaNkulunkulu.\f*; kodwa-ke kuqala ibizo lomuzi laliyiLuzi.
\v 20 UJakobe wasethembisa isithembiso\x + 31.13. 2 Sam. 15.8.\x* esithi: Uba uNkulunkulu ezakuba lami, angilondoloze kulindlela engiyihambayo, angiphe isinkwa sokudla, lesembatho sokwembatha\x + 28.15.\x*,
\v 21 njalo ngibuyele ngokuthula endlini kababa\x + Hlu. 11.31. 2 Sam. 15.7-9; 19.30.\x*, khona iN\nd kosi\nd* izakuba nguNkulunkulu wami\x + Dute. 26.17.\x*,
\v 22 lelitshe leli engilimise ukuthi libe yinsika lizakuba yindlu kaNkulunkulu\x + 35.7,14.\x*; kukho konke ozangipha khona, isibili ngizakunika okwetshumi\x + 14.20. Levi 27.30.\x*.